iven from Healing Gift.  Healing gift increases through the levels  3%, 6%, 10%, 2%, 2%, 2% for a maximum of 16% chance per cast of a critical heal (at the cost of 24AA points)  the first number is our base heal.  I still think HG is cute, but i do like my crits and I have HG at L3 myself (required for our mana free HoT)  The second number set is our heal at Healing Adept 3 10% bonus (at the cost of 12 AA points) the third number set is Healing Adept 6 (at the cost of 25 points)  Healing Adept increases 2%, 5%, 10%, 3%, 3%, 3% for a ending bonus of +19%<br>
<br>
Supernal Remedy  CLR/611: Increase Hitpoints by&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 1450(2900)&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 1595(3190)&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 1725(3450)<br>
Supernal Light  CLR/631: Increase Hitpoints by &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 2750(5500)&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 3025(6050)&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 3272(6544)<br>
Complete Healing  CLR/391: Increase Hitpoints by &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 7500(15000)&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 8250(16500)&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 8925(17850)<br>
<br>
I only post these posts to help everyone understand how AA's effect and improve our class, I am not here to preach the gospel of how one must advance their toon, and hope no one takes me that way.<br>
